  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rabbanak Garden youth hacked to death",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A youth has been hacked to death in Rappanak estate under Udappussala police division.",
        "Police in Udapushsala said that a youth was hacked to death in a clash that took place on the night of (29) between a group of five youths from Rappanak Estate.",
        "A young man named V. Thanoshan (19 years old) was cut with a knife and died in this massacre.",
        "At the same time, a (21)-year-old youth has been admitted to the Nuwara Eliya District Hospital with severe cuts in the group fight, Udapullai police said, who are conducting further investigations into the incident.",
        "In addition, the youth who used the knife in this incident went to the police station and appeared and the two youths involved in the incident were arrested by the police.",
        "Also, the police said that two more youths involved in the said incident have been absconded and have been arrested. After the death investigation of the youth who died in the incident was conducted by the Valappana court judge, the body is going to be taken to the Nuwara Eliya District Hospital for post-mortem.",
        "All of them (29) who were involved in the stabbing incident, were involved in a verbal argument over a love issue after drinking alcohol in the evening.",
        "During this, other youths attacked the young man who had done the knife cutting. The angry young man bought a cutting knife from a hotware in Udapulla city and cut the young men who attacked him.",
        "A youth has died, and a youth has been admitted to the emergency room with cuts, according to preliminary police investigations."
      ],
